Content Management System
Provide
Storage of documents and binary assets (Videos, Images, etc.)
Replication to multiple data centers across the global center
Internal caching

Indexing and full text search​

Document lifecycle (check-in/check-out/publish/delete/undelete)​
Scheduled publish and expiration​
Modification history and audit​
Asset and document versioning​
Role Based Access Control (RBAC) per document and versioning
Multi-tenant
localization(language)

Rich video: multiple resolutions/streaming/audio-tracks/transcripts/closed captions

Rich image:resize/ chop, face detection


